  "text": "The next phase of the knowledge-to-action cycle is to determine the impact of use of knowledge on outcomes specific to health, provider and system. [CITATION_1] Although assessing use of knowledge is important, its use is of particular interest if it influences important clinical tools of measure such as quality indicators.",
